Gnim granna anaithnigh ainiarmartach ro thoill ęscoine fer n-Erenn eter loech &ersir; cleirech do nach frit macsamhla i n-Erinn riam do dhenamh do Thigernan H. Ruairc &ersir; do h-Uib Briuin .i. comarba Patraic do nocht-sharughadh ina fhiadhnuise .i. a chuidechta do shlat &ersir; dream dibh do marbadh &ersir; mac-cleirech dia mhuinntir fein do bi fo chuilebadh do marbadh ann. Is e imorro an iarmuirt do fhass don mhi-gnim-sa conach fuil i n-Erinn comuirce is tairisi do dhuine fodhesta no curo dhighailter o Dhia &ersir; o dhoeinibh in t-olc-sa. In dinsemh-sa tra tucadh for comarba Patraic iss amal &ersir; dinsim in Comdhegh uair adrubairt in Coimdheo fein isin t-shoiscéla; 
Luc. 10:4
Qui uos spernit me spernit, qui mé spernit spernit eum qui mé misit.
